<p>After Ege University Mechanical Engineering Department, he studied Management Sciences at Baruch College, NY and International Management and Marketing at Bahçeşehir University. He is the president of Armaggan A.Ş. (www.armaggan.com) and NAR Doğal Ürünler A.Ş. (www.nargourmet.com); and board member at BoraJet Airlines. He is on the Board of Trustees at Community Volunteers Foundation, and member of board at Turkish Coalition of America Turkey Branch (www.turkishcoalition.org) and Friends of Kitchen Association.</p>